title: Bajaj Auto sales dip 11% in February on export woes
description: Bajaj Auto's exports declined 38 per cent last month at 1,26,935 units, as against 2,03,273 units in February 2022, the company said in a stock exchange filing on Wednesday. Its total wholesales declined by 11 per cent year-on-year to 2,80,226 units in February.
